<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<!--
  Paparcar 2022 brand logo in full colour — blue gradient disc, white car body,
  white stroked wheels. Faithful conversion of 2022/Icon Logo 2022/paparcar_icon.svg.

  Used ONLY as the notification large icon (rasterised to a bitmap), where colour
  is allowed. The status-bar small icon must stay monochrome (see ic_notification_logo).
  Transparent corners (disc only) so it renders circular on any launcher/OEM.
-->
